description: MOVE IN READY CONDO W. PRIVATE DECK & STORAGE | Beautifully updated, well maintained Southie condo blending charm w/ functionality in one of Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods! Enjoy an inviting open-concept layout featuring hardwood floors, cozy living room w/ custom built-ins and an electric fireplace. The stylish kitchen offers granite counters & Stainless Steel appliances. Enjoy effortless living with in-unit Bosch W/D (2023), Central A/C, and generous storage throughout, including a huge approx. 10x10 private basement storage. The private deck offers a perfect spot for morning coffee, evening wine, or container gardening in the city! The bedroom, thoughtfully tucked away from the main living space, is partially enclosed (no door), adding to the open vibe. The bathroom was refreshed with a new vanity in January 2025, adding a modern touch to the space. Ideally located just blocks from Broadway’s restaurants, shops, public transit, Castle Island, and the beach!
